Show HN: Blarb V2 – Ephemeral microblogging that promotes unfiltered sharing
text:
We are excited to announce that we are launching version 2 of Blarb. Blarb is an ephemeral microblogging platform that promotes unfiltered sharing. Anything you share in Blarb gets deleted in 24 hours. Real names are optional, no likes, and no follower count.

New features in version 2: - Improved discovery by introducing explore page. - Instant notifications in supported browsers. - Recent blurbs in the landing page. - Improved UI/UX in some of the pages. - And the most requested Dark mode.

Happy #sharing.

https://blarb.co
